# Choice of Database

## Context and Problem Statement

Database is required to store sensitive information of the visa applicants.

<!-- This is an optional element. Feel free to remove. -->
## Decision Drivers

* Information held will be personal and sensitive
* Capable of holding a large amount of information (for a lot of visa applicants)
* … <!-- numbers of drivers can vary -->

## Considered Options

* MongoDB
* SQLite
* Big JSON file
* … <!-- numbers of options can vary -->

## Decision Outcome

MongoDB, because it is fitting as we will be using node.js, and will working with our other technologies.

<!-- This is an optional element. Feel free to remove. -->
### Consequences

* Good, because it will allow us to implement larger security for the data
* Bad, because 
* … <!-- numbers of consequences can vary -->

